Beautiful one BR/studio in East Harlem (aka Spanish Harlem). Hardwood floors, full kitchen with a small sitting area, full bathroom with bathtub, and queen size bed.

Full access to the apartment via the elevator or stairs. Located on the fourth floor.

I may or may not meet you when you arrive to give you the keys depending on your arrival time.

Very lively, fun and safe neighborhood. Spanish Harlem is a great thriving and growing neighborhood. Great little eateries, bars and long time establishments! Also close to the Upper East Side and a bus ride away or ten minute walk from other Harlem landmarks (Apollo theater, etc)...
